    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>soft cheese</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and a generous grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>white sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
